title: Close to DT Hudson - 2 Bedroom, 1 Bathroom
posting_body: ['Picturesque garden level 2BD, 1BA in an up/down duplex.', 'Rare location just a short walk to DT Hudson and one block to Prospect Park!', '625 Commercial Street, Hudson WI 54016', '-Large open Living room with non-functioning Fireplace (for looks w/ nice brick)', '-Private and Secluded end of a cul-de-sac with only a few more owner-occupant homes as neighbors.', '-Scenic backyard great for hanging out and and socializing and grilling', '-Interior has newer flooring, huge picture windows allowing sunlight into the apartment!', '-Appliances include Fridge & glass top electric Stove', '-Full bathroom w/ oversized sink vanity, Tiled floor and newer tub & shower!!', '-Bonus space with a partial tuck under garage off the back', '-In unit Washer & Dryer', '-Newer forced air furnace and central AC (Included in Rent)', '-Non-Smoking Home', '-One block to Historic Prospect Park overlooking the St.Croix River Valley', 'RENT $1,800.00 (includes ALL utilities).', '** 1-year lease, but option for a shorter 6-month additional $50/month', 'SECURITY DEPOSIT $1,500.00', 'AVAILABLE AUGUST/SEPTEMBER TIMEFRAME', 'This unit is unique and secluded!!']
